      {
        "title": "Cyborg",
        "excerpt": "Name     Tier     Type                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Bone Augmentation                  Novice                                                                            Cyberblade Stance                  Novice                                                                                                    Cybereyes                  Novice                                                                            Skimmer Discs                  Novice                                                                            Cyberblade Slash                  Veteran                                                                                                    Radar                  Veteran                                                                            Thrusters                  Veteran                                                                                                    Diamond Soul                  Master                                                                            Orthoskin                  Master                                                                            Synaptic Booster                  Epic                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Bone Augmentation              Novice                        By heavily reinforcing the structure of your bones, you become more resistant to damage. You gain a bonus to your maximum HP equal to Prof + 2 * your Cyborg level.                                  Cyberblade Stance                              Novice                                       Stance                                 You extend metal blades from your arms and can make cyberblade attacks. These deal 1d8 slashing damage, and have the agile, finesse, and unarmed traits. On a critical success with your cyberblade, if you deal damage, the target takes 1d4 persistent bleed damage.   As long as your Speed is at least 20 feet while in Cyberblade Stance, you can Step 10 feet.                                  Cybereyes              Novice                        You replace your eyes with enhanced cybernetic equivalents. You have darkvision out to 60 feet, and you are immune to the dazzled and blinded conditions.   In addition, you can see into the infrared spectrum, allowed you to see the heat given off by objects. You can tell an object’s approximate temperature just by looking at it. You can see warm objects, such as creatures or large machines, even if the object is invisible or there isn’t any light.                                  Skimmer Discs              Novice                        You gain a fly speed equal to your land speed plus 10 feet. You can only fly up to 10 feet above a solid surface that can support your weight; if you go above this limit you fall at the end of your movement.   As an  Encounter power, you can increase this speed by 30 feet for 1 round.                                  Cyberblade Slash                              Veteran                                             Prerequisites           Cyberblade Stance                    Requirements           You are in Cyberblade Stance                                  You make a fierce swipe with both hands. Make a cyberblade Strike. It deals 2d8 extra damage (3d8 if you’re 14th level or higher), and you can push the target 5 feet away as if you had successfully Shoved them. If the attack is a critical success and deals damage, add your Strength to the persistent bleed damage from your cyberblade.                                  Radar              Veteran                                             Prerequisites           Cybereyes                                  You can sense objects through low-frequency radar waves as well as through visible light. You have radar vision out to range of 120 feet. Your radar vision can detect invisible objects, doesn’t require light, can see around corners, and can penetrate through up to 5 feet of solid stone or 1 foot of metal.                                  Thrusters                              Veteran                                       Daily                                                      Prerequisites           Skimmer Discs                    Duration           10 minutes                                  You activate high-powered thrusters within your Skimmer Discs. For the duration, you can fly more than 10 feet above a solid surface.                                  Diamond Soul              Master                        You have fortified your body and mind against eldritch effects. You gain a +1 bonus to saving throws against magic.                                  Orthoskin              Master                        You replace your skin with an advanced artificial lattice that dissipates the force of incoming blows. You gain a +1 bonus to AC.                                  Synaptic Booster              Epic                        Your skill with weapons lets you attack swiftly at all times. You’re permanently quickened. You can use your extra action only to Strike.",
        "url": "/cyborg.html"
      }
      
